                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <div class="note-box">
                    <div class="note-title">üí° Pattern!</div>
                    <p style="line-height: 1.8;">
                        <strong>di-</strong> becomes <strong>na-</strong> in negation:<br>
                        ‚Ä¢ di<strong>√ßim</strong> ‚Üí na<strong>√ßim</strong><br>
                        ‚Ä¢ di<strong>xw√Ænim</strong> ‚Üí na<strong>xw√Ænim</strong><br>
                        ‚Ä¢ di<strong>b√Ænim</strong> ‚Üí na<strong>b√Ænim</strong>
